Actually, I don’t know why. It exhibits odd properties, mainly the attraction, that could be useful if they could be understood and reproduced. It’s not made of any super metal, and can be destroyed like any other mass of metal objects (melting, crushing, chop to bits). I think the Foundation has kept it around because it’s easy to contain, just stick it in a box and don’t touch it. I think it could very safely be melted down and disposed of; I’ll flip the class to “Neutralized” and write a termination report if people think that’s the best course of action.







